Enemy communication intercepted. Security level elevated.

A summary has been copied and printed to all communications consoles.

messages.body: heya guys appears that your SM is a little out of wack lemmie just BSA it into nonexistance.

messages.body: aye we fixed your SM but i guess you are leaving anyways
